@startuml
title
<size:16><b>UC-08: Checkout and Place Order - Activity Diagram</b></size>
end title

|Buyer|
start

:Navigate to Cart page and click 'Proceed to Checkout';

|System|
:Display order summary (items, quantities, unit prices, subtotal, delivery fee, total);

|Buyer|
:Select or enter delivery address;

:Select delivery method (Standard/Express);

:Review order summary and click 'Place Order';

|System|
:Validate stock availability for all cart items (server-side total);

if (All items in stock?) then (no)
  :Notify Buyer and highlight unavailable item(s);
  :Buyer removes item or updates quantity;
  :Cart preserved;
  stop
else (yes)
endif

:Create Order record with status 'Pending Payment' and reserve stock
 (multi-seller order line groups - BR-12);

:Redirect Buyer to Payment Gateway (UC-09);

|Buyer|
:Complete payment (handled in UC-09);

|System|
if (Payment successful?) then (no)
  :Order remains 'Pending Payment' for 30 minutes;
  :Automatically cancel order and release reserved stock (BR-14);
  :Show payment failure message;
  stop
else (yes)
endif

:Update Order status to 'Confirmed';

:Send Order Confirmation email to Buyer and Order Notification email to Seller;

:Clear shopping cart;

stop
@enduml